三、教學目標 Objectives


生物技術相關產品的應用與開發得以突飛猛進，並對醫學研究、畜牧、植物或並它學門產生重大影響。本課程將建立同學的生物科技相關領域的知識特別註重於其與生活中的相關性,介紹生物技術的源由、理論基礎與應用，提供淺顯易懂的生物技術知識，使同學確切瞭解利用生物科技來改善生活與環境。 


Modern molecular biology makes intensive uses of these techniques in biotechnology. Biotechnology has been applied in areas of medical research, agriculture, environmental ecosystem and so on. Monoclonal antibodies and genetic modified crops have developed, and these products contributed to improve the human life. However, the ethics issues of biotechnological product including gene therapy, stem cell research, and genetic modified crops have been concerned recently. The goal of this course is to introduce theoretical basis and application of biotechnology to undergraduate students. Students are expected to gain basic capabilities in realizing the field of biotechnology. 


